Activist: The
Equal Rights Amendment is a dead
issue now.

05:06.940 --> 05:11.178 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Phyllis Schlafly
was one of
the leading conservative
firebrands of her

05:11.211 --> 05:15.982 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
