early 1960s
with a manifesto for the right,
A Choice,

05:22.455 --> 05:24.224 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Not an Echo.

05:24.257 --> 05:30.030 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
