05:53.620 --> 05:59.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Schlafly said she
was defending
what she called the real rights
of women,

05:59.092 --> 06:03.430 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
